URL: http://localhost:8080

POST запросы
URN: /api/registration/ingredient
JSON:
{
	"origin":"Brazil",
	"name":"Coffee Beans",
	"amount": 20.5,
	"price":12.23
}

URN: /api/registration/beverage
JSON:
{
	"beverageType":"Cappuccino",
	"beveragePrice": 20.5
}

URN: /api/registration/equipment
JSON:
{
	"equipmentName":"Coffee Machine"
}

GET запросы:
URN: /api/request/ingredient?id={id}
/api/request/ingredient?id=af7b8b7e-08de-4626-9f8b-c809929c4cfe

URN: /api/request/equipment?id={id}

URN: /api/request/beverage?id={id}

UPDATE Запросы:
URN: /api/update/beverage
{
   "id": "5f60893c-6a1a-449a-9b05-9a2198a8852c",
   "beverageType": "Latte",
   "beveragePrice": 20.5
}

URN: /api/update/ingredient

{
   "id": "a253a735-fd74-48a2-919b-8c45efa47861",
   "amount": 20.5,
   "name": "Coffee Beans"
}

DELETE Запросы:

URN: /api/delete/beverage?{id}

/**
Описание логики работ
*/

1. POST запрос
{
	"origin":"Brazil",
	"name":"Coffee Beans",
	"amount": 20.5,
	"price":12.23
}
возвращает
{
   "id": "9520c206-c224-4f9c-b632-00286e863d54",
   "origin": "Brazil",
   "amount": 20.5,
   "price": 12.23,
   "name": "Coffee Beans",
   "errors": null
}

2. PUT Запрос - обновляем страну происхождения

{
   "id": "9520c206-c224-4f9c-b632-00286e863d54",
   "origin": "Equador",
   "amount": 20.5,
   "price": 12.23,
   "name": "Coffee Beans",
   "errors": null
}

3. GET запрос с этим ID возвращает объект с новым полем origin

4. DELETE запрос с этим id удаляет этот ингредиент